#############################
# DEMON - unix daemon network
# PROCESS ###################
ADMIN -> posts (ACTION @IT RACE) -> BROOD_IN_FIFO
  BROOD - births DEMON
DEMON -> posts (@FACE) -> ADMIN_IN_FIFO
# ITEMS ########################
ADMIN: udp requests
BROOD: DEMON spawner
ACTION: what is done over iterations
@ITER: array of work to be done
@FACE: DEMON attributes
# FIFO FLOW ####################
ADMIN                                    BROOD
   (actor, @ITER, api)
FIFO_WRITE ============================= FIFO_READ 
                (@FACE)                                   DEMON
FIFO_READ =================================================FIFO_WRITE                                 
%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
% (host09_489)  split 10 files
% (host09_950)  get 100 links
% (host03_321)  sha 1000 files
% (host12_843)  slicr 1000 files
% (host04_732)  split 10 files

# HIVE STRUCTURE ###################################
 
[ ==== /bin /pool /sea /g /k /log /tombstone =====
[ ================================================
[ =================== ZFS NFS ====================
^^      vv     ^^      vv        ^^      vv
^^ host vv     ^^ host vv        ^^ host vv
^^  09  vv     ^^ 03   vv        ^^ 12   vv
**********     *********           *******
** /tmp **
* DEMON3 *
* DEMON2 *
* DEMON1 *
**********
**********
*#######**
*# API #**
*#sha  #**
*#get  #**
*#krip #**
*#split#**
*#slicr#**
*#######**
**********
  |     |
  | UDP |
|         |
( dynamic code )
( actor @iterations )

